  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1320400/" class="title-link">“灵光”乍现的本雅明</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1320400"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/dengjinming/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1854493-73.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/dengjinming/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">春田</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-03-07"
      class="main-meta">2008-03-07 14:03:44</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1320400_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  关于aura一词的译法。现在比较公认的是三种译法：“灵晕”、“光晕”和“灵光”。其中张玉能老师认为翻译成“光晕”最好，理由是可以准确地体现出机械复制时代以前的艺术品的“本真性”和“神秘性”。如果是这样的话，我倒觉得aura更应该翻译成“灵光”。因为它能同时兼顾神学...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1320400/#comments">(19回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">120有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
